v1.0 19th April 2013
  - The first stable release.

v0.3 28th January 2013
  - Added the full API documentation.
  - glGetBooleanv(), glGetBufferParameteriv(), glGetFloatv(),
    glGetFramebufferAttachmentParameteriv(), glGetIntegerv(), glGetProgramiv(),
    glGetRenderbufferParameteriv(), glGetShaderiv(), glGetTexParameterfv(),
    glGetTexParameteriv(), glGetUniformfv(), glGetUniformiv(),
    glGetVertexAttribfv() and glGetVertexAttribiv() now always return tuples.

v0.2 10th December 2012
  - Any object that implements the Python buffer protocol can now be passed
    when a block of memory (i.e. a void *) is expected.
  - Requires SIP v4.14.2.

v0.1 27th October 2012
  - The first release.
